@startuml
title Online Quiz System — Polished Requirement Specification

state StartChoice <<choice>>
state TeacherChoice <<choice>>
state StudentChoice <<choice>>
state DraftChoice <<choice>>
state PostChoice <<choice>>
state ResultChoice <<choice>>
state SelectQuiz <<choice>>
state AnswerQuiz <<choice>>
state SubmitQuiz <<choice>>
state ViewResult <<choice>>
state EndJoin <<choice>>

[*] --> StartChoice

state Register
Register : do / Fill details
Register : exit / Registration successful

state Login
Login : entry / Registered user
Login : do / Enter login credentials
Login : exit / Valid username and password

state "Continue as Teacher" as Teacher
Teacher : entry / Teacher logged in
Teacher : do / Create, edit or save quiz

state "Create Quiz" as CreateQuiz
CreateQuiz : do / Define quiz details
CreateQuiz : exit / Save quiz as draft or post it

state "Save Draft" as SaveDraft
SaveDraft : entry / Teacher wants to save draft
SaveDraft : do / Save quiz as draft
SaveDraft : exit / Quiz saved as draft

state "Post Quiz" as PostQuiz
PostQuiz : entry / Teacher wants to post quiz
PostQuiz : do / Post quiz for students
PostQuiz : exit / Quiz posted successfully

state "View Results" as ViewResults
ViewResults : entry / Teacher wants to view results
ViewResults : do / View quiz results
ViewResults : exit / Results viewed

state Student
Student : entry / Student logged in
Student : do / Select a quiz

state "Select Quiz" as SelectQuizState
SelectQuizState : entry / Student chooses a quiz
SelectQuizState : do / Display quiz details
SelectQuizState : exit / Quiz selected

state "Answer Quiz" as AnswerQuizState
AnswerQuizState : entry / Student answers the quiz
AnswerQuizState : do / Save each answer
AnswerQuizState : exit / Quiz answered

state "Submit Quiz" as SubmitQuizState
SubmitQuizState : entry / Student wants to submit quiz
SubmitQuizState : do / Submit the quiz
SubmitQuizState : exit / Quiz submitted successfully

state "View Result" as ViewResultState
ViewResultState : entry / Student wants to view result
ViewResultState : do / Display quiz results
ViewResultState : exit / Results viewed

StartChoice --> Register
Register --> Login
Login --> Teacher
Teacher --> CreateQuiz
CreateQuiz --> SaveDraft
SaveDraft --> [*]
CreateQuiz --> PostQuiz
PostQuiz --> [*]
Teacher --> ViewResults

Student --> SelectQuiz
SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult
ViewResult --> EndJoin
EndJoin --> [*]
@enduml
